VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \bSELECT\s+\*\s+FROM\b
WHEN EXPR MISSING:LIMIT\s+[0-9]+
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the use of "SELECT * FROM" in SQL queries, which may expose unnecessary or sensitive data, increasing the attack surface.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for SQL Query: Unrestricted SELECT *.
